This project demonstrates a simple Machine Learning workflow using Linear Regression to predict student marks based on the number of hours studied. It covers data preparation, model training, evaluation, prediction, and visualization using Python and Scikit-learn.

The goal is to show a complete beginner-friendly ML pipeline in a clean and reproducible way.

